WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.457 --> 00:00:01.469
Good morning, family.

00:00:03.658 --> 00:00:04.364
I am excited to be with you all again today.

00:00:05.960 --> 00:00:06.231
I have a word for you.

00:00:07.047 --> 00:00:18.867
I was praying and seeking the Lord one night, and about 3:00 AM, the Lord came to me very loudly in my spirit and said, 'Brandon, you are asking Me about who the major leaders in the End Time Army will be.

00:00:18.867 --> 00:00:28.853
' As I was praying about this, He said, 'John Kilpatrick will be one of the major voices in the End Time Army that you can trust and listen to.

00:00:28.853 --> 00:00:36.573
' This was what the Lord spoke to me, so I check in on his ministry every once in a while and listen to see what is going on.

00:00:41.893 --> 00:00:55.219
One of my family members sent me a video that he did a couple of Sundays ago about a word that the Lord gave him in the middle of the night.

00:01:10.900 --> 00:01:11.240
I am putting it all on here to show you that the Lord gave him a warning, telling him about major earthquakes and volcanoes that were going to start to take place.

00:01:16.705 --> 00:01:17.140
I believe what he was seeing was for the United States.

00:01:23.937 --> 00:01:24.791
I am telling you all, I saw a major event taking place; as he pointed out, what the Lord showed him is in Oregon.

00:01:27.160 --> 00:01:27.747
I do not want to go on until you can watch it.

00:01:27.747 --> 00:01:37.200
I want to tell you all this: it is amazing to see when God speaks to people who are prophetic.

00:01:39.813 --> 00:01:45.982
It is like a mirror; it is different, but it is the same because it is the same Spirit of the Lord.

00:01:45.982 --> 00:01:52.590
He speaks to each one of us differently in the way we interpret it, and I think it is amazing.

00:01:52.835 --> 00:01:56.308
I want to encourage you all to watch this whole thing.

00:01:56.308 --> 00:02:02.659
This is a prophetic message for today—a warning for what is coming.

00:02:02.659 --> 00:02:12.780
A major shift and a major shaking are about to take place in this world, and it is not just about America; it is about a worldwide wake-up.

00:02:12.780 --> 00:02:16.879
Jesus Christ is coming, and you better be ready.

00:02:16.879 --> 00:02:19.480
If you are not saved, today is your day.

00:02:19.480 --> 00:02:26.413
You need to get born again, turn, and repent of your sins, for Jesus Christ is coming.

00:02:27.093 --> 00:02:33.531
I want to encourage you all to please watch this whole thing; it will bless you.

00:02:33.531 --> 00:02:39.080
This sermon is amazing, and I hope it blesses you.

00:02:39.080 --> 00:02:50.560
Knowing this first: there shall come in the last days scoffers, walking after their own lusts and saying, 'Where is the promise of His coming?

00:03:08.908 --> 00:03:09.325
For since the fathers fell asleep—the ones who used to be alive and told us the Lord was coming—He hasn't come.

00:03:09.325 --> 00:03:18.314
' All things continue as they were from the beginning of creation without missing a lick.

00:03:27.976 --> 00:03:28.485
The Bible says that they are willingly ignorant.

00:03:34.077 --> 00:03:36.352
They have made up their minds that no matter what they see, they are going to be untouched by it.

00:03:37.660 --> 00:03:48.219
They have made up their minds that no matter what sign is taking place in the world on their televisions and before their very eyes, they are not going to believe.

00:03:48.219 --> 00:04:01.474
They have a blindfold on; they are willfully ignorant of the word of the Lord.

00:04:15.942 --> 00:04:16.164
The heavens were of old and the Earth standing out of the water and in the water.

00:04:32.491 --> 00:04:33.097
It says two things: 'willingly ignorant.

00:04:33.097 --> 00:04:38.011
' Not just ignorant, but willingly ignorant.

00:04:45.766 --> 00:04:47.749
They won't let it penetrate them, won't think on it, won't tell their children, and won't discuss it with their spouse.

00:04:47.749 --> 00:04:56.635
Pastors won't preach it to their congregations; they willingly stick their head in the sand or put a blindfold on and say, 'No, it's nothing important.

00:04:56.635 --> 00:05:11.225
' I saw preachers standing behind the pulpit, and they had oil—this smooth-looking oil—all over their mouths, and it was dripping from their lips.

00:05:11.225 --> 00:05:17.369
They had roaches and bugs crawling in and out of their mouths and laying upon their lips.

00:05:31.464 --> 00:05:31.639
They were crawling in their teeth, and the bugs were crawling in and out of their mouths as they spoke.

00:05:31.639 --> 00:05:41.794
They had a sheen in their eyes; their motives behind what they were preaching were all selfish gain, trying to appease the ears of the people.

00:05:41.794 --> 00:05:53.067
Then I saw the ears of the people, and I could see their ears were being pacified by all these whispers of the things that were happening in the spirit.

00:05:53.067 --> 00:06:01.399
'Everything is going to be good; all things are going to work for your good for those who love the Lord.

00:06:01.399 --> 00:06:09.520
' They were speaking the Word, but they were not speaking what was on God's heart.

00:06:23.404 --> 00:06:24.049
They were speaking things, but they weren't speaking things to make you grow.

00:06:30.720 --> 00:06:37.639
I saw those bugs coming out of their teeth and mouths, and the Lord spoke to me and said, 'Brandon, the preachers are not teaching the meat of the Word to grow My children up into adult stature.

00:06:37.639 --> 00:06:46.373
' And those who are on terrorist watch lists are crossing into our country now every day, many times a day.

00:06:46.373 --> 00:06:54.505
I know that many people coming across our borders are desperate for a new life and a new start, and I understand that.

00:06:54.505 --> 00:06:55.085
I really do.

00:06:55.085 --> 00:07:01.759
I feel sorry for many of them; they are poor, they cannot get healthcare, and they dream of coming to America.

00:07:01.759 --> 00:07:13.909
I can understand they are willing to pay any price to get here, even if it means coming in illegally, and my heart goes out to them.

00:07:20.154 --> 00:07:21.805
But there are many others who have an evil intent to destroy our country and our way of life.

00:07:33.331 --> 00:07:33.726
I want to show you a scripture; it is found in Nahum 3:13.

00:07:37.539 --> 00:07:45.159
I am going to read it in the King James first, and then I am going to read it in the NIV and the New Living Translation.

00:07:45.159 --> 00:07:53.939
Here is the King James: 'Behold, thy people in the midst of thee are women: the gates of thy land shall be set wide open unto thine enemies.

00:07:53.939 --> 00:07:58.670
' In Nahum 3:13 (NIV), it says: 'Look at your troops—they are all weaklings.

00:07:58.670 --> 00:08:01.399
The gates of your land are wide open to your enemies.

00:08:01.399 --> 00:08:06.782
