00:08:17.108 --> 00:08:17.445
The gates of your land will be opened wide to the enemy.

00:08:17.445 --> 00:08:20.063
' That is the southern border.

00:08:21.423 --> 00:08:24.799
I have heard so much talk about the southern border and how this is not happening.

00:08:24.799 --> 00:08:31.369
This presidential candidate said, 'I am going to build a wall and we are going to keep them out.

00:08:31.369 --> 00:08:39.069
' Another president gets elected and he opens them up, and anyone can come.

00:08:39.069 --> 00:08:41.510
It is sickening—it is sickening.

00:08:41.510 --> 00:08:43.790
It is like there is no care anymore.

00:08:43.790 --> 00:08:45.465
We do not care who comes in.

00:08:45.465 --> 00:08:48.270
We do not care if they have bombs.

00:08:48.270 --> 00:09:04.040
We do not care if a hundred of them come in and they all have parts to a nuclear bomb; they will build it and try to have a limited nuclear weapon explode somewhere in this country.

00:09:04.040 --> 00:09:13.180
If that happens, I hate to say it, but we deserve it because we have thrown all caution to the wind.

00:09:13.180 --> 00:09:26.711
Ladies and gentlemen, our country is in great peril, and I think it is time someone stands up and says it.

00:09:26.711 --> 00:09:35.940
Let me read this to you again in the New Living Translation: 'Your troops will be as weak and helpless as women.

00:09:35.940 --> 00:09:39.949
' In other words, the troops will be completely ineffective.

00:09:48.183 --> 00:09:48.394
The gates of your land open wide to the enemy.

00:09:48.394 --> 00:09:49.623
Open wide to whom?

00:09:50.389 --> 00:09:52.509
To people wanting a better life?

00:09:52.509 --> 00:09:56.560
No, open wide to the enemy.

00:09:56.560 --> 00:10:07.668
You see, what happens when you put a blindfold on is the enemy is coming in, and you do not even care anymore.

00:10:07.668 --> 00:10:13.817
Listen: you sow to the wind, you will reap the whirlwind.

00:10:13.817 --> 00:10:19.700
Now I want to show you this scripture in Nahum.

00:10:19.700 --> 00:10:41.440
This is interesting; I think this sums up the Biden administration as well as any scripture I have ever read: 'Behold, I am against thee,' saith the Lord of hosts; 'I will discover thy skirts upon thy face; I will show the nations thy nakedness, and the kingdoms thy shame.

00:10:41.440 --> 00:10:47.154
' In the NIV it says: 'I am against you,' declares the Lord Almighty.

00:10:47.154 --> 00:10:52.440
'I will lift your skirts over your face; I will show the nations your nakedness and the kingdoms your shame.

00:10:52.440 --> 00:11:00.458
' The kingdoms of this world are seeing how weak our president is and how weak his administration is—from the Secretary of Defense to the Secretary of State to the president himself.

00:11:00.458 --> 00:11:02.080
Weak, weak, weak, weak.

00:11:03.159 --> 00:11:09.284
America is in peril, and unless something happens pretty quickly, America is going to be in great peril.

00:11:15.213 --> 00:11:17.013
I saw tens of millions of people coming from the Mexican border—the southern border—trying to invade America over the next year.

00:11:17.013 --> 00:11:20.320
But it wasn't all people from Mexico.

00:11:20.320 --> 00:11:23.896
They were from all over the world.

00:11:23.896 --> 00:11:35.701
I literally saw millions of people coming—millions—so much that whenever you're in a crowd at a football field or a big concert, they're stacked upon stacked, all in lines.

00:11:35.701 --> 00:11:46.180
It's like a sea of people coming across trying to come across the border, but that was like all at once, all trying to come at once, and there was nothing they could do.

00:11:46.180 --> 00:11:58.191
There were so many people seeking God for revival because, as well as I do now, revival is the only thing that will make a difference in America.

00:11:58.191 --> 00:11:59.732
It's the only thing.

00:11:59.732 --> 00:12:03.355
Revival is the cure of all ills.

00:12:03.355 --> 00:12:08.189
We need the government to be on the shoulders of Jesus Christ.

00:12:08.189 --> 00:12:09.939
That's what we need.

00:12:09.939 --> 00:12:12.886
Come on, somebody help me!

00:12:20.080 --> 00:12:20.220
I said we need the government to be on his shoulders.

00:12:20.220 --> 00:12:20.920
Can you shout, 'Amen'?

00:12:23.1000 --> 00:12:25.319
The only thing that's going to save America is an awakening unto God.

00:12:25.319 --> 00:12:35.926
That's the only thing that's ever going to save us is Jesus Christ and preaching him crucified and what he did on that cross for you.

00:12:35.926 --> 00:12:47.765
We need to get born again, we need to get on fire for the Lord, and you start being the salt of the earth and teaching people the word of God.

00:12:47.765 --> 00:12:51.731
That's what's going to change a nation, not politics.

00:12:51.731 --> 00:12:53.565
Politicians are just human.

00:12:53.565 --> 00:13:01.732
Jesus said this in Luke 17: 'As it was in the days of Noah, so will it be also in the days of the Son of Man.

00:13:01.732 --> 00:13:11.391
They ate and they drank, they married wives, and they were given in marriage until the day that Noah entered the ark, and the flood came and destroyed everybody.

00:13:11.391 --> 00:13:18.759
' Likewise, Jesus mentions this; he said, 'I want to bring to your attention, likewise it was also as it was in the days of Lot.

00:13:18.759 --> 00:13:24.199
They ate and they drank, they bought, they sold, they planted, they built.

00:13:24.199 --> 00:13:35.913
But on the day that Lot went out of Sodom, it rained fire and brimstone from heaven and destroyed them all.

00:13:35.913 --> 00:13:41.370
Even so it will be in the day when the Son of Man is revealed.

00:13:41.370 --> 00:13:43.489
' Jesus said this.

00:13:43.489 --> 00:13:47.239
Now, this came out of the mouth of Jesus.

00:13:47.239 --> 00:13:49.480
This is why they didn't like Jesus, because Jesus was a truth-teller.

00:13:54.067 --> 00:14:01.143
He wasn't trying to make nobody mad; he was just saying, 'I'm a watchman on the wall and I see something I think you need to know.

00:14:01.143 --> 00:14:18.560
' And he said, 'As you read about these stories in your scriptures, read and understand: in the last days, it's going to be just like this, like it was in the days of Noah and in the days of Lot.

00:14:18.560 --> 00:14:28.975
' He said, 'As it was in that day, it will be in the day when the son of man is revealed.

00:14:28.975 --> 00:14:31.780
' And then he said, 'Remember this: remember Lot's wife.

00:14:31.780 --> 00:14:35.049
' Now I'm going to talk about these in just a minute.

00:14:35.049 --> 00:14:56.639
So Abram, in chapter 13 of Genesis, said to Lot, 'Let there be no strife, son, I pray, between me and you and between my herdsmen and your herdsmen, for we're brethren.

00:14:56.639 --> 00:14:58.880
Is not the whole land before you?

00:14:58.880 --> 00:15:01.845
Separate yourself, I pray, from me.

00:15:01.845 --> 00:15:05.239
If you'll take the left, I'll go to the right.

00:15:05.239 --> 00:15:10.864
If you don't go to the right, I'll go to the left.

00:15:10.864 --> 00:15:13.947
' And Lot lifted up his eyes.

00:15:13.947 --> 00:15:15.946
He was a narcissist.

00:15:15.946 --> 00:15:24.000
He wanted what was best for him, not what was best for his respectable and honorable uncle Abraham.

00:15:33.450 --> 00:15:33.980
But a narcissist wants what's best for them.

00:15:33.980 --> 00:15:41.702
Could I say this before I go any further?

00:15:41.702 --> 00:15:46.196
That's what's wrong today with leadership in America.

00:15:46.196 --> 00:15:49.742
Just about every one of them is a narcissist.

00:15:49.742 --> 00:15:51.399
Could I say that one more time?

00:15:51.399 --> 00:16:03.194
What's wrong today is the people on subcommittees; they're more interested in that camera being on them and them so-called pinning a witness down so that they can look good.

00:16:03.194 --> 00:16:14.015
But their people at home are more concerned about looking good to the people at home than they are trying to find the truth.

00:16:28.023 --> 00:16:29.376
He said Lot lifted up his eyes and behold the plain of Jordan; it was well-watered everywhere before the Lord destroyed Sodom and Gomorrah, even as the garden of the Lord, which was like Eden.

00:16:29.376 --> 00:16:35.043
It was beautiful, like the land of Egypt, all the way down to a place called Zoar.

00:16:35.399 --> 00:16:47.240
And Lot chose him the plain of Jordan and Lot journeyed east, and they separated from each other.

00:16:47.240 --> 00:16:57.140
Abram dwelt in the land of Canaan, and Lot dwelt in the cities of the plain and pitched his tent toward Sodom.

00:16:57.140 --> 00:16:59.319
Big mistake.

00:16:59.319 --> 00:17:02.400
But the men of Sodom were wicked and sinners before the Lord exceedingly.

00:17:02.400 --> 00:17:22.759
There came a day in chapter 19, verses 1 through 4—I'm going to read this, I can read it better; the word says it better than I can preach it—there came two angels to Sodom at evening, and Lot sat at the gates of Sodom.

00:17:28.559 --> 00:17:30.840
And Lot saw these angels and rose up to meet them, and he bowed himself with his face toward the ground.

00:17:31.695 --> 00:17:40.100
He recognized them as angels, and he said, 'Behold now, my lords, turn in, I pray you, into my house and tarry all night.

00:17:40.100 --> 00:17:46.120
Wash your feet, and you shall rise up early and go on your ways.

00:17:46.120 --> 00:17:52.183
' And they said, 'No, we would rather abide here in the streets.

00:17:52.183 --> 00:18:13.360
' And he pressed upon them greatly, and they turned in unto him and entered into his house, and he made them a feast and did bake unleavened bread, and they did eat.

00:18:13.360 --> 00:18:26.493
Now these angels ate; they were not just spirit beings, ethereal, but they were nebulous—they could digest food, they could eat food.

00:18:29.280 --> 00:18:34.833
And they went to Lot's house and they ate a feast of unleavened bread.

00:18:34.833 --> 00:18:47.939
Now before they laid down that night, the men of the city, even the men of Sodom, compassed Lot's house roundabout, both old men and young men, and all people from all quarters.

00:18:55.644 --> 00:18:56.412
And they called unto Lot and they said, 'Hey Lot, where's those men that came to you this night?

00:18:56.412 --> 00:19:03.349
Bring them out that we may know them,' or bring them out that we may have relations with them.

00:19:08.440 --> 00:19:11.355
Lot went out to the door unto them and shut the door after him.

00:19:27.359 --> 00:19:33.690
The reason he shut the door after him is he didn't want those angels to hear him negotiating with these evil men, because once you ever go to the devil's negotiating table, you're not going to get away until you give something up.

00:19:33.690 --> 00:19:37.480
And notice what he said: he called them 'brethren.

00:19:37.480 --> 00:19:41.060
' He said, 'Brethren, don't do so wickedly.

00:19:41.060 --> 00:19:43.040
' What did you call them?

00:19:43.040 --> 00:19:43.440
Brethren?

00:19:43.440 --> 00:19:45.109
Lot, do you know who you are?

00:19:45.109 --> 00:19:48.022
Do you know that your uncle is Abraham?

00:20:00.788 --> 00:20:07.480
Have you forgotten that your uncle is called the friend of God?

00:20:08.900 --> 00:20:13.008
And you're out here dealing with these wicked, evil sodomites and you're calling them brethren?

00:20:13.008 --> 00:20:16.400
Well, where does that put you?

00:20:29.679 --> 00:20:30.014
And it gets more interesting.

00:20:30.014 --> 00:20:35.570
Listen to this.

00:20:37.420 --> 00:20:37.675
He said, 'I've got two daughters.

00:20:37.675 --> 00:20:40.960
' Well, I have a question: reckon how those daughters felt about that time?

00:20:40.960 --> 00:20:48.320
He closed the door behind him; he didn't want those angels to hear him negotiating with these evil men.

00:20:48.320 --> 00:20:54.860
He said, 'I've got two daughters which have never known a man; they're virgins.

00:20:54.860 --> 00:21:07.636
Let me bring them out to you and you do good to them as you see in your eyes, but to these men don't touch them, for therefore they came under the shadow of my roof.

00:21:07.636 --> 00:21:09.284
' You know what this is?

00:21:18.885 --> 00:21:19.260
Lot did this—yes—willfully ignorant.

00:21:19.260 --> 00:21:21.800
'I'll give you my daughters.

00:21:34.542 --> 00:21:34.844
I don't care what you do to them.

00:21:34.844 --> 00:21:39.270
' In other words, 'I'm willing to put my daughters on the negotiating table.

00:21:47.720 --> 00:21:47.900
Don't touch the angels, but you can have my daughters.

00:21:47.900 --> 00:21:50.000
' Well, what does that mean?

00:21:50.000 --> 00:21:55.290
First of all, the angels are well able to take care of themselves.

00:21:55.290 --> 00:21:55.870
Amen!

00:21:55.870 --> 00:21:58.509
They're well able to take care of themselves.

00:21:58.509 --> 00:22:05.011
As a matter of fact, they're going to see within 24 hours he'll take care of everybody in that whole double twin city, Sodom and Gomorrah.

00:22:05.011 --> 00:22:07.404
But he offered his daughters—willfully ignorant.

00:22:12.559 --> 00:22:12.879
What are you talking about, man?

00:22:18.400 --> 00:22:20.870
Your uncle is Abraham!

00:22:25.980 --> 00:22:26.295
Have you forgotten who you are?

00:22:26.295 --> 00:22:30.533
Have you forgotten that Abraham is the friend of God?

00:22:30.533 --> 00:22:47.120
God said he's his friend, and you're out there talking about these people and you're negotiating with these people and willing to give Uncle Abraham's great-nieces to these men to have their way with them?

00:22:47.440 --> 00:22:48.964
You see what I'm talking about?

00:22:59.813 --> 00:23:00.151
Sin will make a literal fool out of you.

00:23:02.569 --> 00:23:02.751
And they said, 'Stand back!

00:23:02.751 --> 00:23:09.840
' And they said again, 'This one fellow came in to sojourn and he needs be a judge.

00:23:29.980 --> 00:23:30.255
Now we'll deal worse with you than with them.

00:23:30.255 --> 00:23:40.435
' And they pressed sore upon the man, even Lot, and they came to break the door down.

00:23:40.435 --> 00:23:51.160
Such a strong spirit of lust was loose in those cities; it was permeating the atmosphere of those twin cities, Sodom and Gomorrah.

00:23:54.343 --> 00:24:03.794
And these men were burning under that strong spirit of lust, and they came to break the door down because Lot would not present those men to them.

00:24:06.404 --> 00:24:09.325
They were going to come in, break the door down, and get them and rape them.

00:24:10.480 --> 00:24:14.382
And the Bible says the angels put forth their hand, pulled Lot into the house to them, and shut the door.

00:24:14.382 --> 00:24:24.387
And they smote the men that were at the door of the house with blindness, both small and great, so that they wearied themselves to find the door.

00:24:24.387 --> 00:24:40.364
Now, I have something I'd like to say: if I was one of those men of Sodom and there were two men in there that I was interested in, and I saw that they had the power to do that, I'd just say, 'I'm going to the house.

00:24:41.884 --> 00:24:42.705
I don't want nothing to do with that.

00:24:42.705 --> 00:24:45.240
' But they had the power to blind those men.

00:24:56.055 --> 00:24:59.940
The Bible said there was a bunch of them—they surrounded the house, they were violent, they were ready to break down the door—there was a bunch of them.

00:24:59.940 --> 00:25:08.367
But the angels could well take care of themselves, and they blinded those men and they went groping off in the dark.

00:25:15.668 --> 00:25:19.875
And so here's what it says: the men said to Lot, 'Is there anybody else here besides your daughters and sons-in-law and your sons and whatever you have in the city?

00:25:19.875 --> 00:25:22.640
Bring them out of this place.

00:25:22.640 --> 00:25:27.159
' In other words, it was a state of emergency.

00:25:55.085 --> 00:25:55.537
Now, when the angels really saw that it was a state of emergency, the angels said, 'Is there anybody else here besides your daughters and sons-in-law and your sons and whatever you have in this city?

00:25:55.537 --> 00:25:59.740
Go get it and bring it out of this place.

00:25:59.740 --> 00:26:01.373
We're going to destroy this place.

00:26:01.373 --> 00:26:11.824
' They said it: 'We're going to destroy this place because the cry of this sin is waxed great before the face of the Lord, and the Lord has sent us to destroy it.

00:26:11.824 --> 00:26:23.879
' God didn't destroy Sodom and Gomorrah; the angels had been authorized, delegated authority to destroy Sodom and Gomorrah.

00:26:27.339 --> 00:26:27.569
The angels did.

00:26:27.569 --> 00:26:28.599
